Task Manager API (Spring Boot)

A simple RESTful Task Manager API built using Java Spring Boot. This project allows users to create, view, and delete tasks using HTTP endpoints. Itâ€™s designed as a beginner-friendly project to learn Spring Boot, REST APIs, and backend development fundamentals.
