API Endpoints
Get all tasks
Request: GET /tasks
Response:
[]
Add a new task
Request: POST /tasks
Body:
"Buy groceries"
Response:
Task added: Buy groceries
Delete a task
Request: DELETE /tasks/{index}
Example:
DELETE /tasks/0
Response:
Task removed: Buy groceries
